com.google.api.ads.adwords.lib.utils

Interface QueryBuilderInterface.WhereBuilderInterface<QueryT>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ReportQueryInterface.BuilderInterface.ReportWhereBuilderInterface<BuilderT>, ServiceQueryInterface.BuilderInterface.ServiceWhereBuilderInterface<PageT,SortOrderT,BuilderT>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    QueryBuilder.WhereBuilder
    Enclosing interface:
    QueryBuilderInterface<QueryT>

    public static interface QueryBuilderInterface.WhereBuilderInterface<QueryT>
    A builder for the WHERE clause of queries.

    This builder is not thread safe.
